		PRINTFORML 学习pt+{CFLAG:勉強時間 - MEMO_STUDY:0}\@ MEMO_SCHOLAR:0 != BASE:学力 ? ＆学力+{BASE:学力 - MEMO_SCHOLAR:0} # \@
